<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BuchungsbestÃ¤tigung</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1f2937;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
        }
        .email-container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }
        .checkmark {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .checkmark svg {
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            stroke: white;
            stroke-width: 3;
            stroke-linecap: round;
            stroke-linejoin: round;
            fill: none;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #111827;
            margin: 0 0 8px 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #374151;
            margin: 24px 0 16px 0;
        }
        .highlight-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #dcfce7 100%);
            border: 2px solid #86efac;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .date-time {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #166534;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .event-name {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #15803d;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .variation-name {
            color: #4b5563;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .section {
            margin: 32px 0;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #9ca3af;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.2px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .info-grid {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 12px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .info-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .info-label {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .info-value {
            color: #111827;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: right;
        }
        .booking-id-badge {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .action-buttons {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 15px;
            margin: 8px 4px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
        }
        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #374151;
            border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .notice-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7 0%, #fde68a 100%);
            border: 2px solid #fbbf24;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }
        .notice-title {
            color: #92400e;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .notice-box ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
            color: #78350f;
        }
        .notice-box li {
            margin: 8px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .payment-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dbeafe 0%, #bfdbfe 100%);
            border: 2px solid #60a5fa;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }
        .payment-title {
            color: #1e40af;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .payment-box p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #1e3a8a;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 32px;
            margin-top: 32px;
            border-top: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .footer-company {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .footer-contact {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 4px 0;
        }
        .footer-contact a {
            color: #3b82f6;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer-meta {
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-size: 11px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 16px;
            border-top: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                padding: 24px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            .date-time {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            .info-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 4px;
            }
            .info-value {
                text-align: left;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="checkmark">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <h1>Buchung bestÃ¤tigt!</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">{{ siteName }}</p>
        </div>

        <p class="greeting">Hallo {{ userName }},</p>
        <p style="margin: 0 0 24px 0; color: #4b5563; font-size: 15px;">
            vielen Dank fÃ¼r Ihre Buchung. Ihre Reservierung wurde erfolgreich bestÃ¤tigt. Wir freuen uns auf Ihren Besuch!
        </p>

        <div class="highlight-box">
            <div class="date-time">ðŸ“… {{ formattedDateTime }}</div>
            {% if sourceName %}
            <div class="event-name">{{ sourceName }}</div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if variationName %}
            <div class="variation-name">{{ variationName }}</div>
            {% endif %}
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">Buchungsdetails</div>
            <div class="info-grid">
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Buchungsnummer</span>
                    <span class="info-value"><span class="booking-id-badge">#{{ bookingId }}</span></span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Datum</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{ bookingDate }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Uhrzeit</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{ startTime }} â€“ {{ endTime }} Uhr</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Dauer</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{ duration }} Minuten</span>
                </div>
                {% if quantityDisplay %}
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Anzahl Personen</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{ quantity }}</span>
                </div>
                {% endif %}
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Status</span>
                    <span class="info-value" style="color: #10b981;">{{ status }}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        {% set reservationExtras = reservation.getExtras() %}
        {% if reservationExtras|length %}
        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">Service-Extras</div>
            <div class="info-grid">
                {% for item in reservationExtras %}
                    {% set extra = item.extra %}
                    {% set quantity = item.quantity %}
                    <div class="info-row">
                        <span class="info-label">
                            {{ extra.name }}
                            {% if quantity > 1 %} <span style="color: #9ca3af;">({{ quantity }}x)</span>{% endif %}
                        </span>
                        <span class="info-value">{{ (extra.price * quantity)|currency }}</span>
                    </div>
                {% endfor %}
                <div class="info-row" style="border-top: 2px solid #e5e7eb; padding-top: 16px; margin-top: 8px;">
                    <span class="info-label" style="font-weight: 700;">Extras Gesamt</span>
                    <span class="info-value" style="color: #3b82f6; font-size: 16px;">{{ reservation.getExtrasPrice()|currency }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row" style="border-top: 2px solid #3b82f6; padding-top: 16px; margin-top: 8px;">
                    <span class="info-label" style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px;">Gesamtpreis</span>
                    <span class="info-value" style="color: #166534; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700;">{{ reservation.getTotalPrice()|currency }}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if notes %}
        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">Ihre Notizen</div>
            <div style="background-color: #f9fafb; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;">
                {{ notes }}
            </div>
        </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">Ihre Kontaktdaten</div>
            <div class="info-grid">
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Name</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{ userName }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">E-Mail</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{ userEmail }}</span>
                </div>
                {% if userPhone %}
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Telefon</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{ userPhone }}</span>
                </div>
                {% endif %}
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="action-buttons">
            <a href="{{ managementUrl }}" class="btn btn-primary">Buchung verwalten</a>
            <a href="{{ cancelUrl }}" class="btn btn-secondary">Stornieren</a>
        </div>

        <div class="notice-box">
            <div class="notice-title">ðŸ“‹ Wichtige Hinweise</div>
            <ul>
                <li>Bewahren Sie diese E-Mail als Buchungsnachweis auf</li>
                <li>Bei Verhinderung bitten wir um rechtzeitige Stornierung</li>
                <li>Ã„nderungen kÃ¶nnen Sie Ã¼ber den Button "Buchung verwalten" vornehmen</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        {% if isVirtual %}
        <div class="payment-box" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff 0%, #dbeafe 100%); border: 2px solid #3b82f6;">
            <div class="payment-title" style="color: #1e40af;">ðŸŽ¥ Virtuelles Meeting</div>
            <p style="color: #1e3a8a; margin-bottom: 16px;">
                Ihre Buchung findet online statt. Sie kÃ¶nnen dem Meeting Ã¼ber den folgenden Link beitreten:
            </p>
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{ virtualMeetingUrl }}" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin: 0;">Meeting beitreten ({{ virtualMeetingProvider|capitalize }})</a>
            </div>
            {% if virtualMeetingPassword %}
            <p style="color: #1e3a8a; margin-top: 12px; font-size: 13px;">
                <strong>Passwort:</strong> {{ virtualMeetingPassword }}
            </p>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="footer">
            <div class="footer-company">{{ ownerName }}</div>
            {% if ownerEmail %}
            <p class="footer-contact">
                ðŸ“§ Bei Fragen: <a href="mailto:{{ ownerEmail }}">{{ ownerEmail }}</a>
            </p>
            {% endif %}
            <div class="footer-meta">
                Buchung erstellt am {{ dateCreated }}<br>
                Referenz: {{ confirmationToken }}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
